        background-color: transparent !important;

<script>
    (function(scope) {
        scope.toolbar = angular.element('#nr-dashboard-toolbar');
        scope.button = angular.element('#toolbar-toggle-button');
        if(scope.button.length == 0){
            let div = $('<div />');
            let button = $('<button type="button" id="toolbar-toggle-button">Click Me!</button>');
            div.append(button);
            div[0].style.margin = '5px 5px 5px auto';
            scope.toolbar.append(div);
            scope.button = angular.element('#toolbar-toggle-button');
        }
        scope.button[0].onclick = function(){
            scope.send({payload:'click', topic:'toolbar-toggle-button'});
        }
        scope.$on('$destroy', function() {
            scope.button.remove();
            scope.button = angular.element('#toolbar-toggle-button');
        });
    })(scope);
</script>
